      <content:encoded>아침 기온 크게 낮아지고 일부 지역 서리와 눈&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/37L7FTS5TBFPPFHRNEG5G57VAM.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</content:encoded>
